name: CXCallEndedReason
desc: The reason that a call ended.

items.name: case failed
items.desc: An error occurred while attempting to service the call.

items.name: case remoteEnded
items.desc: The remote party explicitly ended the call.

items.name: case unanswered
items.desc: The call never started connecting and was never explicitly ended, such as when an outgoing or incoming call times out.
